{"tid":1547042,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"搞個中秋音樂會激勵士氣好冇","createTime":"2019-09-06T14:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T15:47:32.000Z","uid":178433,"like":25,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"347ec70d3be46007fac3c55bc7c33ad91f21865e","tid":1547042,"uid":178433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T14:00:14.000Z","msg":"我一直以嚟只係和理非，雖然唔係個個活動都有去，但依2個月嚟睇親新聞都會好辛苦，好心痛。相信勇武又好，和理非又好，依幾個月嚟心情一定好壓抑，不如係各區整個<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理非音樂會</span></span>，一齊播歌賞月<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以往中秋都會去公園玩燈籠食月餅，今年我地一齊傾下計，放鬆下，同時比個機會我地好好懷念死去嘅各位義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近好多好歌聽到我好感動(香港國歌，反送中，共臣榜等等)<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家一齊參加好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我願榮光歸香港</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f2d5381ff675aad283b55b77115a46abce57cc","tid":1547042,"uid":178433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T14:01:34.000Z","msg":"幫我推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f3887435aeafbc7aa7e149153cd5d0510300044","tid":1547042,"uid":290761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T14:01:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A8vAmVU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA8vAmVU.jpg&h=305434b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屯門區校友街坊們過黎幫手啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img